parameters:
Pimp: Oh, a prostitute applicant... wait, that's not right.
Get out of here quickly.

Ponhiki no otoko Taka no me no fuego... Hontni osorosh...
Man in a poncho: Fuego with the hawk's eye... Truly
terrifying...
Ponhiki Man: Hey! Who the hell are you!

Fuego, the Hawk-eyed: Please be quiet, or would you like to
be permanently silenced with a knife?
Ponhiki Man: I-I understand... I'll behave!

Fuego, the Hawk-eyed: Please bring me a prostitute from
outside. Although it will be more like a disguised lookout.

Fuego, the Hawk-eyed: Well... this is where the real show
begins.

Fuego, the Hawk-eyed: This basement should be turned into a
gambling den. I want to capture everyone, including the
housemaster, Lance, by any means necessary.
Clea: Leave it to me, I'll be right back.

Fuego, the Hawk-eyed: Please listen to the end of the story!
The opponent, Lance, is not a fool. He must have prepared a
way to escape.

Fuego, the Hawk-eyed: I would like to ask, is there any
skilled gambler among us?
Sophia the Priestess: Hehe, just to indulge a little.

Fuego, the Hawk-eyed: The housemaster Lance here is a big
fan of gambling. If you disrupt the game, he won't be able
to resist and will come running.

Fuego the Hawk-eyed: Once you have successfully lured Lance,
please shout like this.
Fuego the Hawk-eyed: Yes... the Ace of Spades, huh.
Priestess Sophia: I understand. Should I dress up a little?
Fuego, the Hawk-eyed: Yes, that side is more eye-catching.

Fuego with the Hawk Eye: This outfit seems suitable for the
social scene. Now then, are you ready to go underground?

Hawk Eye Fuego: Understood. Please quickly make sure Lance
doesn't escape.

Hawk Eye Fuego: I'm praying for your victory to the goddess
Actina.
Hawk Eye Fuego: Do you have any more elegant clothes?
Hawk Eye Fuego: Please only the clergy members go down.

Fuego, the Hawk-eyed: Thanks to all of you, we were able to
successfully annihilate the large-scale gambling den.

Hawk-eyed Fuego: Here is the promised reward... from Lance
to you.
Cleric Sophia: Please convey my gratitude in my place.

Hawk-eyed Fuego: There are plenty of similar gambling dens
out there.

Hawk-eyed Fuego: At that time, I will rely on you to post
the request on the Valier bulletin board.
